{"tid":598258,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【活佛Viva】網戀對象竟是和尚　少女投訴親密時唸「大悲咒」","createTime":"2018-03-19T11:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T11:29:03.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"480e2a88d2105534d486be602f448f41f3c70e78","tid":598258,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw/images/user_upload/28/a5/f9/28a5f99ec3c10fa7055d98cf64a803f2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.pop.tw.weibo.sina.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fuser_upload%2F28%2Fa5%2Ff9%2F28a5f99ec3c10fa7055d98cf64a803f2.jpeg&h=c649ff11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今時今日，大家要認識新朋友甚至是情人，都可以透過網絡世界認識，不過以這種方法認識陌生人當然有一定風險，除了危及人生安全外，更有機會帶來其他「驚喜」。早前內地就有一名少女分享自己與網戀男友見面的經歷，發現對方竟然是一名和尚！<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qibhfyj30qo0zktdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qibhfyj30qo0zktdd.jpg&h=ba2cb0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFrom:微博/柚子歐尼醬zzz<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qgx9kfj30ku1jitf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qgx9kfj30ku1jitf5.jpg&h=06980152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事件發生於去年，當時少女透過網絡平台認為了一名自稱叫「破戒」男子，雖然對方長相大太出眾，不過性格卻十分討她喜歡，於是兩人開始交往，三個月後男友提意雙方見面，少女認為並無不可，於是答應要求，並由她支付車費。<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qirtpuj30ku1jidlx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qirtpuj30ku1jidlx.jpg&h=42704d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qj8nd5j30ku1ji441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qj8nd5j30ku1ji441.jpg&h=4675b2b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見面對晚大家相約在酒店，少女先到一步，正當她在酒店等待男友時，突然有人按下門鐘，一打開門時竟發現一名身穿袈裟的和尚，原來他就是與自己交往數個月的「破戒」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然男友造型古怪，少女也覺得不妥，但未有抗拒與他親熱，怎料親熱的過程中，男友卻一直唸唸有詞，原來她一直在唸「大悲咒」，令少女感到非常無奈。<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qjkwmej30ku17c42y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qjkwmej30ku17c42y.jpg&h=82977711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qk3pahj30ku1jiwmu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qk3pahj30ku1jiwmu.jpg&h=8156dde2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位男友又經常跟著少女上下班，又指自己要吸收日月精華，無論如何趕對方也不願離開，令少女非常煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n事件於網上引起不少網民關注，不少網民都對於少女的經歷感到非常可笑。<br />\n<br />\n一隻奶黃餃：笑出豬叫 ​ -- 一隻奶黃餃<br />\n<br />\nnelson-天涯closeup：有意思， 哈哈 ​ -- nelson-天涯closeup<br />\n<br />\n王佳雨啊：哈哈哈哈哈網戀嗎分手就割腕 ​ -- 王佳雨啊<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006CXwPIly1fmp8qhpzqgj30ku4ji1g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006CXwPIly1fmp8qhpzqgj30ku4ji1g3.jpg&h=92bddab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180319/1/67/53/%E6%B4%BB%E4%BD%9BViva-%E7%B6%B2%E6%88%80%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%A6%AA%E5%AF%86%E6%99%82%E5%94%B8-%E5%A4%A7%E6%82%B2%E5%92%92-8617676.html?cf=hp-hilite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F1%2F67%2F53%2F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E4%25BD%259BViva-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%2588%2580%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B0%259A-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2594%25B8-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2582%25B2%25E5%2592%2592-8617676.html%3Fcf%3Dhp-hilite&d=GM7QSPNUochv5gqeLjDBhTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=55b5dfd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180319/1/67/53/%E6%B4%BB%E4%BD%9BViva-%E7%B6%B2%E6%88%80%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF